title: Townhouse 3 Bedrooms 2.5 Bathrooms in Aventura
posting_body: ['3 bed 2.5 bath Town House in Eastern Shores Gated Boating Community, that combines access to community Boat Dock along with a private Garden Style Living.', 'This well appointed home is just steps to your boat.', 'Enjoy Ocean Access with no fixed bridges.', 'Pet friendly.', 'Gorgeous entrance tiling, wood flooring.', 'Bedrooms feature built in shelving.', 'Recently installed Mechanized Shutter for Screened in Porch.', 'Very nice kitchen and baths.', 'Utility room with the washer and dryer.', 'Plenty of storage.', 'Two Parking Spots right in front.', 'Dock space is available- boat up to 24-25 ft.', 'Fred Ardjmand / One Stop Realty', 'Licensed Sales Associate', 'Direct:', 'show contact info', 'Coral Gables, Coconut Grove, Pinecrest, Palmetto Bay, Dadeland, Brickell and South Miami rental specialist!', 'Listing Courtesy of SIB Realty LLC']
